cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.MM

The paper focuses on object detection using visual attention and multi-task learning, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of foreground/background segmentation labels and self-attention mechanisms also suggests relevance to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the datasets used in the experiments are related to multimedia (cs.MM), specifically traffic surveillance.
